59
00:03:38,170 --> 00:03:40,010
the backyard of the rich?

60
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:41,650
That’s not what I mean.

61
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,160
I’m just saying

62
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:45,780
we should be more open

63
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,700
to changes.

64
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,760
I agree.

65
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:50,570
I give it my full support.

66
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,940
What’s the point keeping the shabby village?

67
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,860
The money Senwell offers

68
