Senwell is a company

77
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,510
that harbors evil intentions.

78
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,140
How I wish to dig out its boss’s heart

79
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,030
and see if it’s black!

80
