Tonghao,

81
00:04:25,610 --> 00:04:27,200
you eat too much!

82
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:29,370
This is your third bowl.

83
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,980
Taichu hasn’t finished his first.

84
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,290
Cabriolet guy,

85
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,220
how could we let you wash dishes?

86
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,190
Oh, no!

87
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:47,870
It’s late.

88
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:49,360
Go back to hotel and rest.

89
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:51,680
OK.

90
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:54,100
I’m going back now.

91
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,160
OK.

92
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:55,860
See you.

93
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,150
Bye-bye! Bye-bye!

94
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:11,170
What are you looking at?

95
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:13,010
You do the dishes today.

96
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,050
Chen,

97
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,520
I’ve done the dishes for a month.

98
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,890
Look,

99
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:21,580
if I do the dishes with my tender hands,

100
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,290
how could I be able to marry a rich man?

101
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,610
None of your nonsense.

102
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,570
You had case-dough.

103
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:31,850
It’s because you gave us too little.

104
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:32,990
Right, Shengzhe?

105
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:33,860
Yes.

106
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:35,420
Gosh, you guys!

107
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:37,050
One more word and I’ll deduct your money.

108
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:39,420
Well, I’ll do it.

109
00:05:42,650 --> 00:05:43,360
Good man!

110
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:44,460
