120
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:12,170
Would it be too cruel to abandon him?

121
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,500
But, what should we do about him?

122
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,250
We can’t raise him.

123
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:17,800
Look how much he eats. You got a rival.

124
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:22,910
We’re short of a guy in the grocery, right?

125
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:25,090
Why don’t we let him work for us,

126
00:06:25,110 --> 00:06:26,250
