219
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:49,290
By the way,

220
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:51,490
Director Xu,

221
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,130
you have no right to attend the meeting.

222
00:10:56,570 --> 00:10:58,270
