223
00:11:18,770 --> 00:11:19,330
Yunyi,

224
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,240
why don’t you take a leave for a few days?

225
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:23,890
Don’t wear yourself out.

226
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,630
I have no right to rest.

227
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,230
I must complete

228
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,050
Junhao’s projects.

229
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:38,970
