230
00:12:10,530 --> 00:12:13,540
The ring on your finger is so dazzling!

231
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:21,310
Do you remember anything?

232
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,430
It’s just the ring looks so familiar.

233
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:30,500
I think I saw it somewhere before.

234
00:12:32,230 --> 00:12:32,930
Moreover,

235
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,830
it seems you don’t want me to see it.

236
00:12:42,110 --> 00:12:43,920
This ring is mine.

237
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:45,570
You almost robbed it from me.

238
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:49,750
In the past, you didn’t just tell lies.

239
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:51,690
You also robbed things without any fear.

240
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,460
I don’t want you to see it

241
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:55,320
because I’m afraid you may rob it.

242
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,130
I’m that bad,

243
00:12:58,390 --> 00:12:59,450
but you still let me stay.

244
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:01,420
Thank you.

245
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:08,690
It’s called rendering good for evil.

246
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:09,890
I don’t want to blame you.

247
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:12,150
If you’re grateful, work harder.

248
00:13:12,170 --> 00:13:13,920
You may leave when you pay the debt.

249
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:18,360
Qianyu,

250
00:13:19,010 --> 00:13:20,970
can you take me to places

251
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,760
you know that I’ve been to?

252
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:26,680
Maybe my memory will come back.

253
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:27,400
OK.

254
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,990
But my time is precious.

255
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,390
Come on. Get these to Granny Huazi.

256
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:38,210
OK.

257
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:42,320
Do your job.

258
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:44,880
What are you doing?

259
00:13:45,290 --> 00:13:46,470
You haven’t finished your job.

260
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,030
Let me go with you,

261
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:51,420
so I can get on board your job.

262
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,550
Then I can help you

263
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:54,910
and you won’t have to work so hard.

264
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:57,400
All right.

265
00:14:03,090 --> 00:14:04,140
Are you tired?

266
00:14:04,580 --> 00:14:05,850
Let me drive.

267
00:14:07,490 --> 00:14:08,810
You can drive?

268
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,240
It’s a stick shift car.

269
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,480
I think I can give it a try.

270
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:14,680
You sure?

271
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:18,100
Pull over.

272
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,020
Nice!

273
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,090
You have talent in almost everything.

274
00:14:44,710 --> 00:14:45,670
From now on,

275
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:47,140
I can be your driver of your errands.

276
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:42,860
Here it is!

277
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:50,830
This is Devil Forest.

278
00:15:57,050 --> 00:15:57,610
Let’s go.

279
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:19,890
Qianyu,

280
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:21,840
let me take it for you.

281
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,360
Good man!

282
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:27,990
Well, let me tell you.

