00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,740
I used to carry

284
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,870
way more than these.

285
00:16:30,890 --> 00:16:32,330
And I carried them up the hill all by myself.

286
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:33,960
Let’s go.

287
00:16:35,090 --> 00:16:35,660
Careful.

288
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:52,380
The view is great, isn’t it?

289
00:17:03,570 --> 00:17:04,030
Come on.

290
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,660
Granny Huazi!

291
00:17:12,050 --> 00:17:12,890
Granny Huazi!

292
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:14,990
This is Granny Huazi’s home.

293
00:17:15,670 --> 00:17:16,770
Granny Huazi!

294
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:20,530
Qianyu.

295
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:21,240
Granny.

296
00:17:21,650 --> 00:17:22,410
You come.

297
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:24,240
How are you doing?

298
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,410
Great!

299
00:17:26,430 --> 00:17:27,430
Hi, Granny Huazi.

300
00:17:29,090 --> 00:17:29,990
Who is this?

301
00:17:30,710 --> 00:17:31,790
He’s Tonghao.

302
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:32,590
I found him.

303
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:34,530
You found him?

304
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:37,440
Then you’ve found a treasure.

305
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:39,040
It’s true I found him by the road.

306
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:42,560
But I think he’s dumb.

307
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:43,560
He can’t remember anything.

308
00:17:45,770 --> 00:17:48,440
He looks like a clever kid to me.

309
00:17:51,010 --> 00:17:53,470
Granny, predict my luck, please.

310
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:04,590
Have you met someone recently?

311
00:18:06,410 --> 00:18:07,290
Yes, right.

312
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:10,450
He’s the one in your destiny.

313
00:18:10,470 --> 00:18:11,330
Really?

314
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:13,440
However,

315
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,530
you’ll go through a lot.

316
00:18:15,700 --> 00:18:16,990
It’s really him?

317
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:19,650
Who?

318
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:20,850
None of your business.

319
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:22,810
Tonghao,

320
00:18:23,620 --> 00:18:25,110
you can also pick three shells.

321
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,290
When you make the picking,

322
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:29,160
focus on your wishes

323
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:32,350
and what you want to ask.

324
00:18:34,380 --> 00:18:36,350
And then put them on the table.

325
00:18:46,670 --> 00:18:48,280
You really don’t remember anything?

326
00:18:49,370 --> 00:18:50,510
No, I don’t.

327
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,330
Without your previous memory,

328
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:57,190
your life starts anew.

329
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,470
You must be very happy now.

330
00:19:01,230 --> 00:19:01,680
Hmm.

331
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:07,770
Perhaps,

332
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:11,160
it’s because God wants you to stop,

333
00:19:11,390 --> 00:19:12,910
listen to voices around you

334
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:15,340
and feel the happiness and sorrow.

335
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,120
More importantly,

336
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:21,140
he wants you to feel your heart.

337
00:19:21,620 --> 00:19:22,370
You should know

338
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:24,930
not all of us have such an opportunity.

339
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:29,690
People set their eyes on the remote

340
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:33,840
but they tend to ignore their own feelings.

341
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:35,580
Well,

342
00:19:36,820 --> 00:19:37,830
you’re so lucky.

343
00:19:47,630 --> 00:19:48,440
Qianyu,

344
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,200
do you like Taichu?

345
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:54,150
Taichu is great.

346
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:55,570
He meets all Mama Jinzhi’s

347
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:57,360
criteria for a son-in-law.

348
00:19:57,860 --> 00:19:59,440
How could I dislike him?

349
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,700
Even Granny Huazi said

350
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,970
he’s the one I’m bound to meet.

351
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:06,030
Why do you ask?

352
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:08,470
Granny Huazi said

353
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:10,410
the one would appear.

354
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,170
It might not be him.

355
00:20:13,890 --> 00:20:15,490
Not him? You think it’s you?

356
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:17,490
Don’t flatter yourself.

357
00:20:17,510 --> 00:20:18,290
Let’s go home.

358
00:20:18,490 --> 00:20:19,840
It’s getting dark.

359
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:27,320
Qianyu.

360
00:20:28,330 --> 00:20:29,110
Tonghao!

361
00:20:53,470 --> 00:20:54,840
Are you alright, Qianyu?

362
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:57,300
Are you a pig? You’re so heavy.

363
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:58,080
Get up.

364
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:03,910
What is it?

365
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:06,110
I think I hurt my foot.

366
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:07,750
Don’t move.

367
00:21:21,520 --> 00:21:22,350
I think it’s OK.

368
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:24,290
No bone damage.

369
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,560
What should we do now?

370
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,490
Don’t worry.

371
00:21:30,510 --> 00:21:31,950
We can call for help.

372
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:50,600
No signal here.

373
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:59,440
What now?

374
00:21:59,990 --> 00:22:01,410
Seldom would people

375
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,190
come to Devil Forest.

376
00:22:03,210 --> 00:22:04,760
Look, we don’t have any supply.

377
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:06,040
And no phone reception.

378
00:22:07,510 --> 00:22:08,640
If we wait to be found,

379
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:11,050
we’ll become mummies in the end.

380
00:22:11,070 --> 00:22:12,190
If I die,

381
00:22:12,210 --> 00:22:15,200
what will happen to Shengzhe and Mama Jinzhi?

382
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:17,580
Am I going to leave all the debts

383
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:20,490
to Mama Jinzhi like my dad did?

384
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,800
Shengzhe is so little.

385
00:22:22,820 --> 00:22:24,930
It’s gonna be fine. I’ll think of something.

386
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,460
I haven’t made enough money

387
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:30,140
or worn fashionable clothes,

388
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,670
or gone to karaoke,

389
00:22:31,690 --> 00:22:33,260
or played in the amusement park,

390
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:35,500
or had a boyfriend.

391
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,950
And I’m going to die.

392
00:22:36,970 --> 00:22:39,450
That’s so unfair.

393
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:43,620
God, why do you punish me so?

394
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:47,000
I’ve never done anything evil.

395
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:49,640
Promise me. Let me get out. I…

396
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,290
All right. We’ll be fine.

397
00:23:13,670 --> 00:23:14,430
What are you doing?

398
00:23:15,120 --> 00:23:15,970
I’m telling you.

399
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:18,610
Don’t take advantage of my vulnerability.

400
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,360
I have strong arms.

401
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,480
I could punch your teeth out.

402
00:23:26,170 --> 00:23:27,570
What advantage is there to take?

403
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,120
What?

404
00:23:30,210 --> 00:23:31,650
Do you have sight problems?

405
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:32,930
Not at all.

406
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,300
Show me then.

407
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:35,990
Go away. Stay away.

408
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:43,270
I’m kidding.

409
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:46,700
You aren’t so afraid now, right?

410
00:23:48,730 --> 00:23:50,290
Kind of not so afraid.

411
00:23:53,130 --> 00:23:54,710
But what should we do?

412
00:23:59,050 --> 00:23:59,740
All right.

413
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:01,360
Don’t think about that.

414
00:24:02,050 --> 00:24:03,080
Let me see your foot.

415
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,990
Chen, did you make a fortune?

416
00:24:07,010 --> 00:24:08,570
You cooked so many ribs.

417
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:10,360
All small ribs!

418
00:24:16,570 --> 00:24:18,360
This is your sister’s favorite.

419
00:24:19,290 --> 00:24:20,860
She works hard recently.

420
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,370
Wait until she’s back.

421
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:27,140
Mom, just one piece.

422
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:28,210
I’m hungry.

423
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:29,660
I’m starving.

424
00:24:30,110 --> 00:24:32,020
Grandpa Li came to buy laundry detergent just now

425
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:34,320
but I didn’t have the strength to get it for him.

426
00:24:35,810 --> 00:24:37,820
Mom, you’re the prettiest mom in the world,

427
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:38,750
the best mom ever.

428
00:24:38,910 --> 00:24:40,760
I can’t believe you’re so beautiful.

429
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,010
One rib, OK?

430
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:45,590
OK. OK.

431
00:24:45,610 --> 00:24:46,150
OK.

432
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:48,190
Just one piece.

433
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:50,250
OK.

434
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:51,860
It’s OK. I can massage on my own.

435
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,530
Don’t move.

436
00:24:54,610 --> 00:24:55,960
You must lift your foot high

437
00:24:56,740 --> 00:24:57,720
so that blood flows backward.

438
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,990
Otherwise, it would keep swelling up.

439
00:25:01,120 --> 00:25:02,080
How are you going to do that alone?

440
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,320
Does it hurt?

441
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:29,320
Hang in there.

442
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:43,060
Do you feel better now?

443
00:25:44,530 --> 00:25:47,230
I can’t believe your massage

444
00:25:47,250 --> 00:25:48,450
is professional.

445
00:25:55,490 --> 00:25:56,730
Come here. Turn around.

446
00:25:57,020 --> 00:25:59,430
= Money Bag Grocery =

447
00:25:59,430 --> 00:26:01,080
It’s dark.

448
00:26:02,190 --> 00:26:04,180
Why hasn’t Qianyu come back?

449
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,000
Shengzhe,

450
00:26:06,020 --> 00:26:07,160
call your sister now.

451
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:15,430
What’s up?

452
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,810
She didn’t answer.

453
00:26:17,870 --> 00:26:19,850
Should we eat the ribs now?

454
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:24,250
Don’t you think your sister will be sad for that?

455
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,480
I wouldn’t get any when she comes back.

456
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:30,890
Call her! Again, right now!

457
00:26:44,390 --> 00:26:45,740
It’s late.

458
00:26:46,380 --> 00:26:48,170
Mama Jinzhi and Shengzhe

459
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:50,050
must worry about us so much.

460
00:26:53,590 --> 00:26:54,910
Let’s check around the pit

461
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:57,250
tomorrow at dawn

462
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:58,570
and find a way out.

463
00:27:00,010 --> 00:27:01,770
We don’t know if we could find one.

464
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:05,120
In fact, I don’t believe we could.

465
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:14,240
Let me tell you a story.

466
00:27:18,360 --> 00:27:19,290
Once upon a time,

467
00:27:20,320 --> 00:27:22,310
there was a drought-struck frog.

468
00:27:22,330 --> 00:27:23,620
It dug up for water.

469
00:27:24,530 --> 00:27:26,590
It kept digging.

470
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:28,880
However, in the end, it dug out a stone.

471
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:32,170
So it gave up.

472
00:27:34,250 --> 00:27:36,670
Later, it died of thirst.

473
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:41,810
In fact, there’s a spring beneath the stone.

474
00:27:42,660 --> 00:27:45,670
If it moved the stone away, water would flow out.

475
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:50,480
Therefore, don’t give up at crisis

476
00:27:51,100 --> 00:27:52,710
and you’ll find hope in desperate situation.

477
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:03,000
Don’t give up at crisis

478
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:07,080
and you’ll find hope in desperate situation.

479
00:28:10,930 --> 00:28:13,410
Tonghao, you’re good at great stories.

480
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:17,090
Trust me.

481
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,310
We’ll get out of here safe.

482
00:28:31,140 --> 00:28:32,000
Look!

483
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,130
So many stars!

484
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,580
True. So many stars.

485
00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:41,410
I never knew

486
00:28:42,040 --> 00:28:44,170
the stars above Devil Forest

487
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,240
are so beautiful.

488
00:28:47,670 --> 00:28:49,130
What’s your horoscopic sign?

489
00:28:49,710 --> 00:28:50,440
Taurus.

490
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:53,110
Taurus…

491
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:58,240
Give me your hand.

492
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,060
Hold out a finger.

493
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,080
Look,

494
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,460
these five stars

495
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:15,340
form a triangle,

496
00:29:16,010 --> 00:29:17,690
like a bull’s head.

497
00:29:18,950 --> 00:29:20,170
That’s Taurus.

498
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:23,250
You can see it only at this season.

499
00:29:26,630 --> 00:29:27,660
I saw it!

500
00:29:28,330 --> 00:29:29,980
So that’s Taurus?

501
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:34,440
What about yours?

502
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:44,870
I don’t know.

503
00:29:47,390 --> 00:29:49,650
Sorry about that.

504
00:29:52,610 --> 00:29:53,420
It’s OK.

505
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:58,200
I can rewrite my life.

506
00:29:59,910 --> 00:30:02,110
It’s an opportunity so many people can’t get.

507
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:05,630
From now on,

508
00:30:06,410 --> 00:30:09,050
I’ll choose my birthday,

509
00:30:10,020 --> 00:30:11,520
my horoscopic sign,

510
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:12,620
my friends,

511
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,780
and my families.

512
00:30:16,430 --> 00:30:17,130
Qianyu,

513
00:30:18,940 --> 00:30:21,680
you’re the first person I met
after I lost my memory.

514
00:30:22,970 --> 00:30:24,230
You’re my friend,

515
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:25,180
my family,

516
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:27,300
and the most important person to me.

517
00:30:32,930 --> 00:30:33,850
But…

518
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:37,230
Are you cold?

519
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:44,860
I’m trying to fight cold with my fat.

520
00:31:12,450 --> 00:31:14,400
I’ll do everything I can to protect my friend

521
00:31:14,570 --> 00:31:15,600
and my family.

522
00:31:54,410 --> 00:31:55,010
Mom,

523
00:31:58,380 --> 00:31:59,500
have something to eat.

524
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,970
Otherwise you’ll collapse.

525
00:32:07,490 --> 00:32:08,570
I have no appetite.

526
00:32:14,670 --> 00:32:17,530
It’s late. Who is it?

527
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:19,720
Mr. Ziqian.

528
00:32:21,570 --> 00:32:22,360
Ziqian.

529
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:22,970
Yunyi.

530
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:24,280
Ziqian.

531
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:25,710
It’s late. What are you doing here?

532
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:29,490
I heard you had trouble sleeping.

533
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:31,750
So I bought you two sleeping lamps.

534
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:34,090
Thank you.

535
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:39,690
Thank you for what you did recently.

536
00:32:40,990 --> 00:32:42,130
Don’t mention it, Aunt Jiang.

537
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:45,390
I’ll take care of the family and the company.

538
00:32:45,910 --> 00:32:46,570
Don’t worry.

539
00:32:52,990 --> 00:32:54,770
Don’t go back tonight.

540
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:58,170
It’s late. It’s tiresome to drive back.

541
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:01,650
I’ve been keeping your room for you.

542
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,250
Mrs. Lin often cleans up.

543
00:33:04,850 --> 00:33:05,400
OK.

544
00:33:07,410 --> 00:33:08,670
Let me install the lamps for you.

545
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:26,900
Mr. Ziqian,

546
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:28,530
I’ve made your bed.

547
00:33:28,950 --> 00:33:29,860
You can go to sleep.

548
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:31,490
OK.

549
00:33:32,350 --> 00:33:33,920
When they’re asleep, I’ll go to bed.

550
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:35,740
Good night.

551
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,200
OK.

552
00:33:38,470 --> 00:33:39,470
I’ll leave you.

553
00:34:13,160 --> 00:34:14,260
This insolent girl!

554
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,750
When you’re back, I’ll beat you up.

555
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:23,930
Jerk!

556
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,630
You took advantage of me while I was asleep.

557
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:27,970
Stay away from me.

558
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,990
I’m going to marry a rich man.

559
00:35:31,310 --> 00:35:33,860
Please keep proper distance.

560
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:39,660
You hugged me last night.

561
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:43,290
You said you were cold and slept in my chest.

562
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:46,390
I couldn’t help but putting up with you.

563
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,100
I…

564
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:54,140
I just have bad habits in sleep.

565
00:35:57,230 --> 00:35:58,130
From now on,

566
00:35:59,290 --> 00:36:00,150
keep safe distance.

567
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,750
What should we do now?

568
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:29,130
I think there’s an exit.

569
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:30,960
Maybe it could lead us out.

